title: 2019 fantasy baseball surprises and letdowns
text:
In the latest episode of the Rotoworld Baseball Podcast, D.J. Short and Drew Silva wrap up the 2019 MLB season by detailing some notable fantasy baseball surprises and letdowns.

Please rate and subscribe if you enjoy what you're hearing. You can contact the show at rotoworldbaseballpod@gmail.com or on Twitter via @drewsilv or @djshort.
